This paper involves the use of a neural network structure and iterative optimization for clustering, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also deals with uncertainty and conflict management, which are topics in decision making and reasoning under uncertainty (cs.SI) and Dempster-Shafer theory (cs.DS).
